name: Elements (DigiCode66 Games)
description:
Welcome to Elements! This is a game where you must reach Sky Castle as you have been told that something is wrong in Sky Island and your answers are in Sky Castle. This game is just a prototype of what the actual product maybe and I am not sure that if I will finish the game or not. 

Game Controls
Left Arrow=Move left,Climb Ladders Left
Right Arrow=Move right,RightClimb Ladders
Z=jump
X=run
Up Arrow= Climb Ladders Up
Down Arrow= Climb Ladders Down
